query: SELECT dim_date.d_year, supplier.s_city, part.p_brand1, SUM(lineorder.lo_revenue - lineorder.lo_supplycost) AS profit FROM lineorder AS lineorder JOIN dim_date AS dim_date ON lineorder.lo_orderdate = dim_date.d_datekey AND (dim_date.d_year = 1997 OR dim_date.d_year = 1998) JOIN supplier AS supplier ON lineorder.lo_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey AND supplier.s_nation = 'UNITED STATES' JOIN customer AS customer ON lineorder.lo_custkey = customer.c_custkey AND customer.c_region = 'AMERICA' JOIN part AS part ON lineorder.lo_partkey = part.p_partkey AND part.p_category = 'MFGR#14' GROUP BY dim_date.d_year, supplier.s_city, part.p_brand1 ORDER BY dim_date.d_year, supplier.s_city, part.p_brand1
